    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces and add to a bowl with your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up so that the hake is fully coated in the spices</p>",
