      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, chop your<strong> coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Pick your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop them finely, discarding the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
