        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>mint</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> with a small squeeze of<strong> lemon</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Grind to a fine paste, then add your <strong>mayo</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your<strong> mint chutney</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don't have a pestle & mortar, chop everything very finely!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
