    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> topped with the<strong> wilted spinach</strong>,<strong> spiced hake </strong>and<strong> tomato salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the<strong> mint chutney</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
